apps.title: Hinge Dating App: Match & Date
apps.description: HINGE, DESIGNED TO BE DELETED Hinge is the dating app for people who want to get off of dating apps. With profiles that show your personality through text, photos, video, and voice, you have unique conversations that lead to great dates. And it’s working. Currently, people on Hinge go on a date every three seconds. Additionally, in 2022, we were the fastest-growing dating app in the US, UK, and Canada. HOW WE GET YOU OFF HINGE When it comes to online dating, people are so busy matching that they’re not actually connecting, in person, where it counts. Hinge is on a mission to change that. So we built an app that’s designed to be deleted. Here’s how: * We quickly learn your type. You’ll only be introduced to the best people for you. * We give you a sense of someone’s personality. You’ll get to know potential dates through their unique answers to prompts, as well as information like religion, height, politics, dating intentions, relationship type, and much more. * We make it easy to start a conversation. Every match begins by someone liking or commenting on a specific part of your profile. * We want you to feel confident about meeting people in person. Selfie Verification makes it easier for daters on Hinge to ensure that they are who they say they are. * We ask how your dates are going. After exchanging phone numbers with a Match, we’ll follow up to hear how your date went so we can make better recommendations in the future. The app is free to use. Members looking to see everyone who likes them or send unlimited likes can upgrade to Hinge+. To access additional features, including enhanced recommendations and priority likes, we offer HingeX. apps.title: Bumble Dating App: Meet & Date
apps.description: The dating app bringing people closer to love Bumble is the dating app where people meet, make connections, and start their love stories. We believe meaningful relationships are the foundation of a happy, healthy life — and we're here to help you find yours with a commitment to member safety and tools that empower confident dating. Match with the right people, date, and find meaningful connection Bumble is a free app for meeting singles and building connections grounded in mutual respect and trust. Whether you’re ready to find the one or date for fun, Bumble can help you connect with real people to build something authentic. As champions of love, we prioritize creating a space where our members feel respected, confident, and empowered to make connections - Our members are at the heart of everything we do - We put safety first — so you can date with confidence, knowing you’re connecting with verified matches - Respect, courage, and joy guide how we show up — and inspire others to do the same Try our free features — built to make dating easier - For better connections, conversations, and dates, personalize your profile with interests and prompts to showcase who you are, what you’re into, and what you’re looking for - Trust that the person you’re talking to is real with ID Verification - Feel confident with expert-backed dating advice designed to help you succeed - See what music you bond over by linking your Spotify account - Video chat and share your favorite pictures with your matches to get to know them better - Chat with peace of mind — knowing that when you’re talking to new people, all messages must meet our community guidelines - Get extra reassurance by sharing the details of your meetups with someone you trust - If you’re ever in need of a dating break, hide your profile with the Snooze Mode (you'll still keep all your matches) Want even more ways to connect? Bumble Premium unlocks extra features to boost your dating experience - See everyone who likes you - Use Advanced Filters like “What are they looking for?” to meet people who share your values, hobbies, and goals - Rematch with expired connections — so you don’t miss out on a great potential date - Browse anonymously with Incognito Mode and only seen by who you want to see you - Extend your matches by 24 hours - Swipe as much as you like to meet more people - Tap into dating scenes around the world with Travel Mode - Stand out and get noticed with free SuperSwipes & Spotlights, refreshed weekly Inclusivity is key At Bumble, we promise to support and include all forms of love: straight, gay, lesbian, queer, and beyond. We want everyone in our community to feel safe and welcome. So no matter how you identify, if you're looking for a place to chat, date, and find real love, we’ve got what you’re looking for. --- Bumble is a free dating app to download and use. We offer optional subscription packages (Bumble Boost & Bumble Premium) and non-subscription, single, and multi-use paid features (Bumble Spotlight & Bumble SuperSwipe). Your personal data is securely processed in line with our privacy policy and applicable laws—be sure to read our privacy policy and terms and conditions. https://bumble.com/en/privacy https://bumble.com/en/terms Bumble Inc. is the parent company of Bumble, Badoo, and BFF, social networks, and dating apps free to download and use.

apps.title: Plenty of Fish : Dating App
apps.description: The best dating app to let you really be you and choose how you want to date online. Forget the days of awkward online dating and become a POF member, where you can come exactly as you are. We’re here to help you create the same magic online that you would IRL. We know online dating isn’t one-size-fits-all, so we let you choose your own adventure and connect with other singles in a way that feels right for you. Whether you’re new to dating or just seeking a fresh start, we’ve got lots of options to make finding your person actually fun. What you can do on POF is what makes us different: - Selfie Verification so you can see who’s really behind the profile - Search for exactly what you want - Restrict your first message count so you don't get 1 and 2 word intros - Come as you are and find other real, down-to-earth people like you Just click that install button to get started! POF is part of the Match Group portfolio which also includes Tinder, Match.com, Hinge, OkCupid, Meetic, The League, BLK, Chispa, Upward, Stir and OurTime. All photos are of models and used for illustrative purposes only.

apps.title: Tinder Dating App: Date & Chat
apps.description: MATCH, CHAT & DATE. IT STARTS WITH A SWIPE™. With 97+ billion matches to date, Tinder® is the top free dating app and the best place to meet new people, with safety features that work to help you date more safely. Looking for love? An open relationship? Trying to find a date or new friends to chat with? Connect with local people everywhere on Tinder and get the best out of your dating experience: Come As You Are: Whether you're straight, gay, bisexual, or anything in between, you can be who you are and find who you want on Tinder. Date Beyond Photos: Share your interests and learn more about your matches to get the conversation started. Seek What You’re Looking For: Set your relationship goals and make connections on your terms. HOW TINDER WORKS It’s easy and fun to find new people on Tinder®. Express yourself to make your personality shine in your profile and stand out to potential matches. Answer a prompt, share a little about you, and show face in your pics to increase your match-making potential. Use the Swipe Right™ feature to Like and the Swipe Left™ feature to Nope. If they Like you back, It’s a Match! And with our double opt-in feature, it’s only a match if the interest is mutual. PUT SAFETY FIRST Try some of our safety features to help you make connections more confidently: - Share My Date: Share date plans with friends and fam, so they know who you’re planning to meet up with and where - Get Photo Verified: Verify your photos to help potential matches know it’s really you in that cute pic & increase your chances of matching - Are You Sure / Does This Bother You: Tinder detects inappropriate language so people think twice before sending a disrespectful message - Report a Profile: Quickly report and block profiles with suspicious activity or inappropriate behavior - Block Contacts: Take control and block anyone (like an ex) you don’t want to see on the app - Video Chat: Hitting it off in chat? Test your online dating chemistry and meet new people from home! TRY TINDER PLUS - Unlimited Likes for you to catch feelings for as many new people as you want - Use Passport Mode™ to match and chat with locals anywhere in the world before you arrive - Unlimited Rewinds to undo your last Like or Nope - Go Incognito and be seen only by the people you Like EXPERIENCE TINDER GOLD - Get everything in Tinder Plus™, and try it out for a week before you commit to a monthly subscription - See who Likes You and match with them on the spot for faster connections - Monthly Boost puts your profile to the top for 30 minutes to help increase your profile views - Weekly Super Likes, because sometimes you really, really Like someone UPGRADE TO TINDER PLATINUM Get most of Tinder’s premium features: Join Tinder Platinum™ to get your Likes prioritized with potential matches, send them a compliment before matching, and more. So what are you waiting for? Join millions of people worldwide! Tinder offers the most daters, increasing your chances of finding exactly what you're looking for. Download the best free dating app today! --------------- If you choose to purchase Tinder Plus®, Tinder Gold™, or Tinder Platinum™ payment will be charged to your Apple account, and your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time by going to your settings in the App Store after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active subscription period. If you don’t choose to purchase Tinder Plus®, Tinder Gold™, or Tinder Platinum™, you can simply continue using Tinder for free. All photos are of models and used for illustrative purposes only. Privacy: https://www.gotinder.com/privacy Terms: https://www.gotinder.com/terms Visit: https://www.tinderlove.com/

Use our profile tips and rely on icebreakers and compatibility checks to chat and flirt. Whether you’re into casual connections or one of the relationship seekers, there’s room for everyone. Finding love or a relationship may not be the ultimate goal. But exploring and meeting new people always feels fun. Check out Hily's top dating features: • Compatibility Quiz to connect on a deeper level • Fun zodiac synastry test to see if your stars align • Profile verification and safety team for confidence in your dating • Photo and profile tips to find a date with no stress • Personalized icebreakers to chat and flirt like a pro We believe that dating apps should make online dating easy and fun. Use Hily your style and date as you are, meet new people and make lots of new, fun connections. Get the app, build your profile, chat with local singles, meet up for real – and get the relationships you’re looking for! You can look for true love or just network and meet up with local friends. Because dating is not just about romance—it’s also about sharing life, meeting new friends, and feeling seen. Whether you're looking for something meaningful or something casual, Hily helps you connect with people near you who are smart, kind and intelligent enough to know that real connection starts with being yourself. Stay in touch with us! • Share your experience by leaving your feedback at apps@corp.hily.com • If you're wondering about safety and privacy, take a look at our Terms of Service at https://hily.com/terms and Privacy Policy at https://hily.com/privacypolicy We want dating apps to be fun again. Get Hily dating app to enjoy the ride on your terms!

apps.title: Duet Dating App: Chat & Meet
apps.description: Ready to find that special connection? Welcome to Duet - a new dating app featuring REAL profiles for all kinds of interests. Whether you're a gamer, fitness enthusiast, foodie, fashionista, cat person, meme expert, cinephile or a bookworm, you'll find someone whose interests and passions strike a chord with you. NO SCAMMERS WITH DUET'S 100% MANDATORY VERIFICATION Tired of endless swiping only to fall prey to scammers and catfish? Duet introduces a foolproof 100% mandatory face verification, as reliable as banking security. No more fake profiles — we love authenticity and real connections, just like you. Plus, Duet's 24/7 moderation team is always on alert, tackling any scam reports swiftly. DISCOVER YOUR PERFECT MATCH WITH DUET'S SMART TAG Duet's Smart Tag digs deeper than superficial similarities, covering your interests, traits, opinions, and habits. This multifaceted self-description enhances connections and guarantees a match based on an in-depth understanding of each person. SHARE YOUR VOICE WITH DUET'S VOICE PROMPT Voices are full of emotion and depth — share your 30-second story, open up about yourself, and invite meaningful conversations with one another. DISCOVER LIKE-MINDED PEOPLE IN UNIQUE WAYS Had enough of swiping? Duet Blind Date connects you with similar individuals through engaging new features. ► Duet's Dating Quiz matches users who pick similar answers, breaking the ice and encouraging further conversation. ► Duet's Personality Test unveils your romance compatibility score and relationship strengths. ► Duet Clic randomly pairs you with someone based on your location and zodiac sign compatibility, letting fate take the wheel! UPGRADE TO DUET PREMIUM FOR EXCLUSIVE FEATURES ► See Who Likes You: Instantly match and chat with your secret admirers. ► Unlimited Likes: Enjoy Duet without any limits on likes you send. ► 5 FREE Crushes daily: Boost your chances of matching. ► 1 FREE Turbo monthly: Amplify your profile visibility. Unlock more premium perks for the ultimate dating journey! JOIN THE DUET SUPREME CLUB TO ENJOY YOUR PERSONAL FILTER Duet Supreme includes all 9 Duet Premium privileges with extra exclusive privileges: ► Message Before Matching: You can send 3 Praises directly to people you like ► Advanced Filters: You can filter by height, education, purpose and popularity to only see your type ► Daily Picks: Duet will pick the most popular users and recommend to you everyday Duet Premium and Supreme purchases are charged to your iTunes account and will be auto-renewed unless disabled in-app 24 hours before the current period ends. apps.title: Badoo Dating: Meet New People
apps.description: Boost your dating confidence with Badoo— the dating app that makes it easy to express your true self. It’s an encouraging, safe space that’s designed to help you make more meaningful connections. How? By keeping it simple, helping you take action with confidence, and giving you the features and support you need to find whatever you’re searching for. Whether that’s dates, a long-term relationship, new friends, or chats. Plus, with our latest tech that aims to block fake, scam, and spam accounts, you can say hello to a fun and authentic dating experience. Download Badoo to take your dating confidence to another level." Back yourself On Badoo, it’s all about celebrating you and staying true to your needs. With our various features, it’s easy to put yourself out there with confidence. Trust your experience Badoo is a platform that prioritises authenticity. Profile photos can be verified and there are strict user guidelines in place. How Badoo works Focusing on who you are and what you want, here are some features making it easier for you to meet your kind of people: -Advanced Filters: Finesse your search, and save your time -Profile Questions: Easily champion your personality - People Nearby: Meet daters around you - Encounters: Straight forward swiping, right to connect and left for skip - Video Chat: Connect with your matches through face to face video calling - Verified profiles: We have a three-step verification process which, once completed, you can choose to only interact with other verified profiles and find friends - Blur intimate photos: Using AI, our Private Detector feature detects explicit photos and will let you decide if you want to view or block the image - Deception Detector: Our new tech that aims to block fake, scam, and spam accounts, so you can have a fun and authentic dating experience" Go Premium Maximise your dating experience. When you upgrade to Badoo Premium, you’ll unlock plenty of features that will make it even easier to find meaningful connections: - See who's already liked you - Find exactly what you’re looking for with unlimited Advanced Filters - Get your messages read first - Send unlimited likes - Control who sees your profile with Invisible Mode - Undo accidental left swipes - And much more... The price varies by country and may change without notice, but you can always see the exact price in the app. We will charge your card and your subscription will be automatically renewed unless you deactivate the automatic recharge a minimum of 24 hours before the end of your current subscription period. Badoo Premium is flexible and adapts to your needs - you can cancel your subscription at any time. For more information, read our Privacy Policy and Terms of Use: https://www.badoo.com/privacy https://badoo.com/terms Bumble Inc. is the parent company of Badoo, along with Bumble and Fruitz

With over 12 million members around the world, WooPlus is one of the most welcoming and inclusive dating communities—and it's growing every day. Translate profiles and messages, and send messages in any language with cutting-edge translation. OUR VALUES 1. LOVE, KINDNESS, EMPATHY Boo is an accepting, tolerant, and judgment-free space for everyone. Unlock functionalities by being a good person and earning love, our social credit system. 2. Embracing your authentic self starts when you realize that every personality has its flaws, that there are others who share your same personality, and that you are not alone. 3. apps.title: Grindr - Gay Dating & Chat
apps.description: Grindr is the world’s #1 free dating app serving the LGBTQ community. If you’re gay, bi, trans, queer, or even just curious, Grindr is the best and easiest way to meet new people for friendships, dates, and whatever else you’re looking for. On a trip? Grindr is an indispensable tool for LGBTQ travelers—log in to meet locals and get recommendations for bars, restaurants, events, and more. With Grindr in your pocket, you’ll always be connected to other LGBTQ people around you and have your finger on the pulse of what’s happening. Ready to get started? Creating your profile is easy, and you can share as much or little about yourself as you like. Within minutes you’ll be ready to connect, chat, and meet up with people near you. Grindr is faster and better than ever: • See people nearby based on your location • Chat and share private photos • Add tags to share your interests • Search tags to find others based on their interests • Create private albums to share (and unshare) multiple photos at once • Filter your search to find what you want • Star your favorites and block others • Report people easily and safely Looking for even more? Upgrade your Grindr experience to XTRA for more features, more control, and more fun: • No 3rd party ads • See up to 600 profiles at once • View only people who are online now • View only profiles with a photo • Filter by position, relationship status, and more Want the ultimate Grindr experience? Upgrade to Grindr Unlimited for our most premium features: • Unlimited profiles • Full access to your Viewed Me list • Incognito mode - browse profiles without being seen • Unsend messages and photos • All XTRA features Need help? If you are experiencing any issues, you can get support by contacting us through https://help.grindr.com Grindr Ads: Grindr (excluding XTRA and Unlimited accounts) includes third-party advertising, which involves the sharing of limited data with our Ad/Marketing partners as described in our privacy policy. Grindr does not share any of your Grindr profile information with Advertising or Marketing partners. You can adjust your third-party advertising privacy settings within the app at any time. Grindr Subscriptions: Your subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Your iTunes account will automatically be charged at the renewal price within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period unless you change your subscription preferences in your App Store account settings. You can manage your subscriptions at any time through your App Store account settings after purchase. Any unused portion of a free trial period will be forfeited when making a purchase of an auto-renewing subscription. Grindr, Grindr XTRA & Grindr Unlimited are for adults 18 years and older only. Profile photos depicting nudity or sex acts are strictly prohibited. Terms of Service: www.grindr.com/terms-of-service/ Privacy Policy: www.grindr.com/privacy-policy/

apps.title: PURE: Anonymous Dating App
apps.description: PURE is a dating app for curious people to show up in their most playful version of themselves. It’s a space to be honest with your intentions and clear in your boundaries. Connect with like-minded community to create and explore new exciting experiences in a safe and supportive space. Let your imagination go wild and get ready for amazing dates! * HOW PURE WORKS? Everything starts with Personal Ads. To see other people in the feed, you need to post your Ad. Write what kind of experience you are looking for and find someone who would share the same experience with you. Be creative and original with your ads, that's always appealing. * IN PURE ALL BORDERS ARE OPEN Paris, New-York or London? You can check any city worldwide and meet people from PURE community from around the globe. * WHAT HAPPENS IN PURE STAYS IN PURE Photos self-destruct right after being seen, and in case someone takes a screenshot, you will get a notification about that. Also, all chat messages, including photos and audio, shared in chats cannot be saved to the phone's gallery. * OUR MISSION IS TO KEEP PURE A PURE EXPERIENCE Safety of our community is one of our key priorities. We are constantly improving our algorithms to find and get rid of scam and spam accounts, also our system sends automatic alerts on trigger words that might be used by scammers, so don't be surprised in case you will get a warning. Keep chatting anonymously via PURE and do not switch to other messengers. You know what they say: better safe than sorry. PURE uses auto-renewing subscriptions — you have to subscribe to get inside. Here’s what you should know about PURE subscriptions: - If you choose to purchase a weekly, monthly or annual subscription you will be able to go online and interact via chats with other users during the chosen subscription period. The prices may vary per country and are subject to change with a notice. Prices are clearly displayed in the app. - All subscriptions renew automatically unless you cancel at least 24 hours before the end of the current subscription period without any limitations. - Auto-renewal can be canceled at any time by going to your settings in the Apple Store after the purchase. - All personal data is handled under PURE’s privacy policy https://pure.app/content/en/privacy - Terms and conditions: https://pure.app/terms/

apps.title: Taimi LGBTQ+ Dating & Chat App
apps.description: Taimi is an all-inclusive LGBTQIA+ dating app for people who are 18 and older. We have disrupted online dating with the concept of fluid dating. Simply put, it is free from the limits of the hetero-dating model. That’s why we’ve been able to create amazing experiences for more than 25 million registrants worldwide. apps.title: Yubo: Chat Meet & Make Friends
apps.description: Welcome to Yubo – the ultimate social platform for making new friends all over the world! With millions of users worldwide, we’re all about connecting you with like-minded people in a fun and safe place! FEW THINGS YOU NEED TO KNOW ABOUT YUBO 1) SWIPE TO MAKE NEW FRIENDS: Use our swipe feature to find new friends who are online and share the same interests! With just a swipe, you could meet your new bestie! 2) CHAT WITH FRIENDS WORLDWIDE: One of the coolest things about Yubo is that you can chat with people from all over the world! Whether you're feeling silly, want to sing, dance, or chat about your day, Yubo has got you covered! 3) FIND YOUR TRIBE: At Yubo, finding your tribe is key to making lasting connections! Thanks to the Tags, you can find other people into gaming, beauty, sports, music, dance, and so much more! So, whether you’re a gamer, a makeup artist, or just looking for like-minded friends, Yubo has got you covered! 4) IT’S FREE: Yubo is totally free to use! 5) IT’S SAFE: We take your safety seriously. That's why we've designed many features and tools to ensure you can use Yubo safely. So, what are you waiting for? And, as always, feel free to contact us on Instagram (@yubo_app) or Twitter (@yubo_app) with any questions or feedback! Yubo is free to download and use, which will never change for our main features. However, if you want to get the most from Yubo, you can subscribe to one of our optional products, the Yubo Power Pack or Yubo Elite Pack. We offer weekly, monthly, and 3-month subscriptions, giving discounts on the weekly price. The prices may vary per country and are subject to change without notice. Prices are clearly displayed in the app. * Payment will be charged to your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase. * Your subscription will automatically renew itself unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. * Your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours before the end of the current period. * You can manage your subscriptions and turn off auto-renewal by going to your Account Settings in the iTunes Store. * If offered, if you choose to use our free trial, any unused portion of the free trial period will be forfeited when you purchase a subscription to that publication, where applicable * If you don’t choose to purchase Yubo Power Pack or Yubo Elite Pack, you can continue using and enjoying Yubo for free. Your personal data is securely stored on Yubo - be sure to read our privacy policy and terms and conditions: https://yubo.live/legal/privacy https://yubo.live/legal/terms

raw_data.description: High standards? Keep them that way. The League is a selective dating app offering its members a curated “Batch” of potentials each day, rather than an unlimited stream of profiles. Designed for motivated daters who would rather be single than settle, The League strongly believes that 3 quality matches are better than 100 bad ones. So say goodbye to endless swiping and keep those standards sky-high— because while your mother might call you picky, we call you self-aware. The League uses an application process to ensure a well-balanced, highly engaged community of people with real motivation to find a meaningful long-term relationship. You can use The League for free or upgrade to a subscription to unlock additional benefits. Subscribers see more profiles each day, and thus, enjoy 40% more matches on average. Subscription Details: Payment will be charged to Apple Account at confirmation of purchase. Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Subscriptions may be managed and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to Account Settings after purchase. See our terms of service at https://www.theleague.com/terms-of-service-en/ and and privacy policy at https://www.theleague.com/privacy-policy-en/ All photos are of models and used for illustrative purposes only.

apps.title: Holy — Christian Dating App
apps.description: Holy (formerly United Young) is an app to meet people who love Jesus, made by married couple Kathleen & Jonathan. The app lets you connect with an inspiring selection of Christians near you every day. See someone you’re interested in? Wave at them. If they wave back, we will connect you both, and you can chat! • Find a friend within the Christian community. • Read why people say Jesus matters. • Share your testimony and Bible inspiration. • Find inspiration in the faith journey of people near you. • Discover people in similar seasons of life. Note: Christ-honoring dating is only available to those who are single and of age 18 and upward. We welcome everyone who confesses Jesus Christ as their Lord and Savior, and considers themselves a Christian (confessing the Nicene Creed) to join! We seek to connect the greater Christian community, and are united in our love for Jesus. Whether you are Catholic, Nondenominational, Evangelical, Anglican, Baptist, Reformed, Orthodox, Pentecostal, Lutheran, Methodist, or are just at the beginning of your journey with Jesus, you are welcome to join our diverse community of believers! This app was inspired by the call to unity (in Ephesians 4 & John 17) and the call to love and encourage one another (in Hebrews 10 & 1 Thessalonians 4). In addition, we were greatly inspired by Dietrich Bonhoeffer’s book “Life Together”. Bonhoeffer beautifully describes how we can see Jesus more clearly in the lives and testimonies of our brothers and sisters. ** Winner of both Jury and People’s Choice Awards at NYC Redeemer Presbyterian’s Center for Faith & Work’s Startup Pitch Night. ** Holy is free to download and use. This is made possible by members who generously subscribe to our Supporter plan. Supporting Holy lets us further the app and its mission, and gives access to extra features. Supporter benefits include: • See all received waves in one place. • Go back with 48 hour history. • Send priority messages. • See when chats are read. The price and duration of our Supporter subscriptions are clearly displayed in the app. You can manage and cancel your subscriptions by going to your account settings on the App Store after purchase. By downloading or using the Holy app, you kindly agree to our Privacy Policy and Terms of Use: https://www.holy.app/privacy https://www.holy.app/terms We hope you are inspired, and would love to hear from you! :) Connected in Christ, Kathleen & Jonathan Email: support@holy.app Web: https://www.holy.app

apps.title: Mingle2 - Dating & Meet People
apps.description: Discover Mingle2 – Your Gateway to Meaningful Connections!!! Dive into the vibrant community of Mingle2, where making meaningful connections is fun and effortless. Whether you're looking to find new friends, engage in lively chats, or start a romantic relationship, Mingle2 has you covered. Our app and website are among the largest free online dating services, tailored to suit everyone's needs. Enjoy a seamless experience with features designed to help you connect with like-minded individuals and build lasting relationships. Discover why millions are choosing Mingle2 and start your journey today! WHY JOIN MINGLE2? ⋅ Instant Matches: Receive daily match recommendations tailored to you. ⋅ Global Search: Connect and chat with people from around the world. ⋅ Nearby Connections: Easily find and chat with people in your local area. ⋅ Unlimited Likes: Send as many likes as possible to maximize your chances. ⋅ Free Premium Features: Access features like sending direct chats without waiting for a match, with daily limits to prevent misuse. ⋅ Social Features: Enjoy Nudges, view Who's Online, and many other features to help form meaningful relationships. ⋅ Privacy Protection: Your personal information is secure, with easy account deletion and blocking options. ⋅ Photo Verification: Enhance authenticity by verifying your account with a photo pose, helping to limit fake profiles and improve trust. HOW TO USE MINGLE2? ⋅ Sign Up: Create your profile in just 30 seconds! ⋅ Search Locally or Globally: Find someone special in your area or anywhere in the world. ⋅ Start Chatting: Begin conversations with people you like. ⋅ Filter Preferences: View members that match your criteria. ⋅ Online Users: Chat with online users worldwide. ⋅ Mutual Match: Play and meet someone wonderful. ⋅ Other Features: Explore constantly improving features designed to help you find meaningful relationships, regardless of your location or relationship goals. SECURITY & PRIVACY ⋅ Scam Fight System: Our advanced system combines automatic tools, human oversight, and AI for 24/7 monitoring and continuous improvement. ⋅ Dating Safety Hub: Safety tips to protect yourself, avoid scams, and safeguard personal information are displayed on every chat screen. ⋅ 24/7 Customer Support: Chat directly with our support team anytime. ⋅ Report Suspicious Profiles: Use the "report" feature for automated and human review. ⋅ Absolutely NO Seeding Profiles: We do not create fake profiles or associate with scammers. Although high-tech scammers may generate fake profiles, we monitor and remove them swiftly, constantly improving our system to combat them. FREE vs PAID FEATURES With Mingle2, you can enjoy premium features for free with daily limits to prevent misuse. Send direct chats without needing mutual matches, and utilize features like Rewind and Nudge. Additionally, you can send unlimited likes, maximizing your chances of finding a compatible partner. On the free plan, ads are shown to help fund the product's maintenance and development. You don't need to pay to enhance your search or find a meaningful relationship. However, a paid subscription is available to save you time and add convenience, offering an even smoother experience. MinglePlus Subscription: ⋅ 3-month subscription: $29.99 ⋅ 6-month subscription: $47.99 ⋅ 12-month subscription: $69.99 Notice: ⋅ Prices are in U.S. dollars, may vary internationally, and are subject to change. Payments will be charged to your iTunes account and automatically renew 24 hours before the current subscription period ends (3/6/12 months). You can turn off auto-renewal through your Apple device or iTunes store. If auto-renewal is turned off, your subscription will expire at the end of the current period. ------- Contact Support: https://mingle2.com/welcome/contact_us Privacy Policy: https://mingle2.com/welcome/showPrivacy Terms of Use: https://mingle2.com/welcome/showTOS Community Standards: https://mingle2.com/welcome/code_of_conduct

apps.title: Flava: Casual Dating & Chat
apps.description: Flava brings you to a new level of online dating. - It enables anonymous registration via Apple ID - We care about your privacy: Your chat messages and photos cannot be saved by anybody. We'll notify you and hide the screen if someone tries to record or make a screenshot. Your private messages are being taken care of and will never leave the app. - Private photos: You can make photos in your gallery private. They will be seen only by your matches and those whom you already liked. - Incognito mode: Switch to incognito mode and you won't appear in the general search, only people you liked will be able to see you! You must be 18 years of age to use Flava. Flava Premium Subscription: - If you purchase a Flava premium subscription, you will see who liked you, the last time users were active, you will get unlimited likes, you will be able to make photos private, turn on incognito mode and also filter the search by active users. - The subscription is made from your Apple ID account and renews automatically. Deleting the app does not automatically cancel the subscription. - All subscriptions auto-renew until you cancel them at least 24 hours before the end of the paid period. Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, indicating the cost of the renewal. - Once you purchase a subscription, you can manage it and turn off auto-renewal in your iTunes subscription settings - Personal data is processed in accordance with the privacy policy: https://flava.app/privacy/ - Terms of use: https://flava.app/terms/

apps.title: Raya
apps.description: Our focus at Raya is to provide members with access to exciting people and opportunities around the world. We are a private community where people come to connect for dating, networking, and friendship. – Prospective members may download the app and submit an application. Once submitted, applications are placed in queue and reviewed continually. An applicant's status can change from "waitlisted" to "accepted" at any time. Once accepted, members have the option to purchase a 1, 6, or 12 month auto-renewing membership and will have full functionality of the entire service while their subscription is active. Raya's community values – trust, respect, and privacy – are core to the membership experience. Members who act in a manner that is not reflective of these values and other community guidelines may have their accounts suspended or terminated. Similarly, Raya exhibits those values as a company by giving members full control over their visibility within the community at all times and ensuring that personal information is secure and never shared, among other things. Initial payment is charged via iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase and auto-renewals are charged within 24 hours prior to the end of the applicable period. Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time through iTunes Account Settings. Any subscription cancellation will be effective at the end of the applicable period. For more, please see our Terms of Use and Privacy Policy: https://www.rayatheapp.com/privacy https://www.rayatheapp.com/terms

apps.title: BlackGentry: Black Dating App
apps.description: BlackGentry dating app is a members-only dating app that makes it easier to meet ambitious and intentional singles. BlackGentry is designed to foster a high-quality community where members can meet, match, and build lasting relationships. Every profile is reviewed by the membership committee before being accepted. Prospective members can download the app and submit an application. Once submitted, applications are placed on a waitlist and are reviewed by the membership committee. An applicant’s status can change from “waitlisted” to “accepted” at any time. We prioritize detailed, polished profiles with classy photos that reflect effort and profiles that align with our community standards. Acceptance is not guaranteed, and profiles that don’t meet our criteria will not be approved. Our community values are kindness, respect, integrity and growth. BlackGentry is open to everyone and our mission is to provide an online community that makes it easier for singles to establish healthier connections and relationships. All members can chat with their matches for free and also send a limited number of Direct Messages per day. Members can choose to subscribe to Deluxe or VIP to enable more features. Subscription options include 1-month, 3-month, 6-month, and 12-month plans. Prices are in U.S. dollars, may vary by country, and are subject to change without notice. Subscriptions will be charged to your Apple account at confirmation of purchase and your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current subscription period. Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time by going to your Apple Account settings. Subscriptions will auto-renew unless turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription to that publication, where applicable. Subscriptions are tied to only one BlackGentry account and cannot be used by multiple accounts. Terms: https://blackgentryapp.com/terms-of-service/ Privacy Policy: https://blackgentryapp.com/privacy-policy-2/ We will be glad to see all your feedback at contact@blackgentryapp.com

apps.title: Dating and Chat - Sweet Meet
apps.description: Sweet Meet makes dating for singles easy and fun! Our online dating app lets you meet locals and go on dates with them in real life. You see couples dating whenever you leave the house and wish that could be you? Well, one of the perks of local dating is that you get to make quick plans after chatting a little, without too much effort from either party. No need to drive for an hour or get train tickets to a different city. Go grab coffee with your date, catch a movie at the local theater or get dinner and drinks after work; no need to be on chatting apps for weeks in a row! Matching, chatting, setting up dates - as easy as they can be. Sweet Meet is the dating app for relationship seekers. Today’s society may make you feel like wanting to find a family is silly or outdated, and you may have noticed that most chat apps are designed to find dates predominantly. At Sweet Meet, we value family and think you should be able to find yours. Girls, you can match with caring and amazing men on Sweet Meet and find a husband. Same goes for men! Start swiping find a wonderful woman you want to build a life with. Date with the intention to find a family! We promise you, even in this day and age, true love is not impossible to find. You could meet your soulmate today and build a real life fairytale with them! Create a fun social network. We know making friends as an adult is not easy, when you’re out of school and everyone is busy with their own lives. That’s exactly why we’re here to help! Unlike other chat apps, on Sweet Meet, you can meet new people and find friends who match your crazy! Start chatting with your matches today, make fun plans and go on adventures with your new friends. What we forget sometimes, a soulmate doesn’t have to be a romantic partner. With a little help from our app, you can make new friends who can become family. All you need to do is download the app on your phone, set up your profile with your favorite photos and a little bit about yourself, and start swiping. Once you get a match, message them to break the ice and start getting to know each other. Feeling a connection? Use the momentum to set up a date that could possibly mark the beginning of something wonderful! But you don’t have to take our word for it. You’ve got nothing to lose, so why waste any more time? Your future partner or best friend could be only a swipe away! Any town, any country – we embrace people from all over the world. We securely store your personal data. Please read our privacy policy and terms of service : https://sweetmeet.me/policy.html https://sweetmeet.me/agreements.html

apps.title: CatholicMatch Dating App
apps.description: CatholicMatch -- Faith Focused Dating for Catholics You want to marry someone who shares your faith. But you’re not finding anyone. That’s where we come in. Helping single Catholics meet is the reason we exist. Over 1.5 million people have signed up for CatholicMatch, and they’re looking for sacramental marriage. Thanks to our focus on community and faith resources, not only do our members meet other singles for faith-focused dating, but most come away from CatholicMatch with lifelong benefits: an increased knowledge of their faith and new Catholic friends for years to come. Technology keeps giving us new ways to connect, and CatholicMatch has been at the forefront of this expansion for the past twenty years. While we’ll never know the exact number, based on what we do know, thousands and likely tens of thousands of sacramental marriages have started on CatholicMatch Experience Matters There are many dating apps out there, and while they may share common features, too many times the experiences are wildly different. We want your dating experience on CatholicMatch to be dependable and useful. So, we place a priority on dating with the goal of sacramental marriage, not just dating to date. Additionally, we try to provide an experience that not only encourages purposeful dating, but also promotes values like respect, charity and compassion. In addition, our customer service team is dedicated to accompanying our members in every way possible. They not only provide answers to questions and concerns in a timely manner, they also review all photos and profiles uploaded on the site. Plus, they complement our automated security by manually reviewing questionable accounts and behaviors. Although there is no perfect system, providing a safe and enjoyable experience is one of our top customer service priorities. Subscription Prices** 1-month subscription: $29.99 6-month subscription: $89.99 12-month subscription: $119.99 **Prices are in U.S. dollars, exclude any applicable sales tax, may vary in countries other than the U.S., and are subject to change without notice. Please note that with all subscriptions: * Your subscription payment will be charged to your iTunes account. * Your subscription will automatically renew and your iTunes account will be charged for renewal 24-hours prior to the end of your current one/six/twelve month subscription period. * You can turn off the auto-renewal of your subscription through the App Store on your Apple device or through the iTunes store on your computer. Once you turn off auto-renewal, your subscription will expire at the end of the current subscription period. We give users a private and secure experience, a friendly and diverse community, and more features than any other gay dating app. We’re dedicated to protecting our members’ data and improving user experience, so you’ll never see banner ads on SCRUFF, and we won’t sell your data to shady 3rd party companies. MAKE REAL CONNECTIONS 30+ million users, no spambots Find exactly the people you like with search and filters View, Woof, and chat with people SCRUFF Match connects you with the people you like Click "I'm Interested" on a profile and SCRUFF will let you know if there's a mutual attraction EXPRESS YOURSELF Share your story with multiple profile pics, rich profiles, private albums, hashtags, and more Let others know what you’re into with profile details like preferences and safer practices Comprehensive pronoun and gender identity options put you in control of your identity A SMARTER, SAFER EXPERIENCE 24/7 support for our community, including in-app links to our Safety Center We never share your data with 3rd party ad networks or data aggregators like Google or Facebook Message history, photos, and videos sync across your devices and never get lost VERIFIED PROFILES Let others know you're real by verifying your profile photos Complete the process in seconds and receive a verification badge on your profile Know whose photos are real by looking for the badge on other profiles VIDEO CHAT A fun and flirty way to get to know each other before you meet Prefer to keep it virtual? Video chat has you covered MATCH Every day, SCRUFF Match shows you a new stack of profiles who are looking for people like you Swipe left to pass, right if you’re interested - if it’s a match, we’ll let you both know Choose “Ask later” if you’re not sure about them, and we’ll show them again tomorrow SCRUFF EXPLORE Browse the top LGBTQ parties, prides, and festivals around the globe RSVP, see who else is going, and find your squad Traveling? Let others know when you'll be in their area and chat with local members before you arrive Question? Comments? We’re available any time at support.scruff.com. apps.title: Waiter: less dating, more love
apps.description: Waiter is the dating app that gives you the best chance to find love Forget wasting hours swiping through endless profiles. Forget matches that never lead to a single conversation. Forget fake profiles that aren't verified. QUALITY OVER QUANTITY Waiter only shows you people who truly match with you because one real match is worth more than a thousand pointless ones. Every day, our Matchmaking AI selects 3 people for you to meet, and you get to choose the one you'd like to connect with (for free). 2 MILLION MEMBERS Join a community of people looking for serious relationships, not just one-night stands. Meet singles who want to take the time to truly get to know each other over time and aren't just there to seduce, please or flatter their ego. 500,000 MATCHES ALREADY MADE It’s becoming harder to find someone genuine these days, but the good news is that real gems still exist. Waiter has already brought together thousands of people who struggled to find the right person on typical dating apps. YOU DESERVE THE BEST Finding love is the most beautiful thing that can happen. Waiter has created the best possible conditions to help you get there. Give yourself every chance to love and be loved. LET CLOÉ BE YOUR GUIDE From the moment you sign up, you’ll have support from our godmother Cloé, who will accompany you throughout your search. If you have any questions, you can message her directly in the app. Cloé can analyze your profile, your photos, and give you tips to break the ice with your matches. You’re in good hands. READY FOR LOVE AT FIRST SIGHT? Give yourself every chance to meet someone amazing with Waiter. Your personality matters just as much as your looks, your passions and values too. These are the things that make you truly unique, and they can’t be judged in a single second. Trust us to help you find that rare gem. Good luck from the entire amazing Waiter team.

Look no further than Topface – the premier online dating app for friendships, romance, and everything in between. ◆ Comprehensive Profiles: Create a personalized profile with descriptions, photos, name, and age to showcase your personality and interests. ◆ People Nearby: Discover interesting individuals nearby with our feature, simplifying local connections. ◆ Advanced Search: Use intuitive filters to find matches aligned with your preferences. ◆ Seamless Chat: Engage in meaningful conversations with mutual interests, fostering connections effortlessly. ADVANTAGES: ○ Extensive User Base: With over 170 million profiles, find someone who interests you. ○ Quick Registration: Start your dating journey hassle-free. ○ Global Reach: Connect with people from diverse backgrounds. ○ People nearby: Discover nearby users for spontaneous meetups. ○ Intuitive Interface: Navigate Topface easily for an enjoyable experience. VIP BENEFITS: Enhance your Topface experience with VIP status: ◆ Invisibility Mode: Browse profiles discreetly. ◆ Free Adorations Sending: Express interest freely. ◆ Blacklisting: Control interactions by blacklisting users. ◆ View Profile Guests: See who visited your profile. ◆ Personal Profile Design: Customize your profile to leave a lasting impression. Join Topface today and explore endless possibilities. Whether you seek companionship, romance, or more, let Topface guide your journey to meaningful connections. Download now and start your adventure! You can choose the most convenient subscription period for VIP: for 1 week, 1 month, 3 months, 6 months, and 1 year. The subscription cost starts from $2.99. You can renew any of these subscriptions automatically: Your iTunes Account will be charged after you confirm your subscription. If you would like to unsubscribe, you'll have to do so no later than 24 hours before the end of your current subscription's expiry date. The renewal payment for your subscription will be charged to your account within 24 hours of your current subscription's end period. Your subscription's renewal can be turned off in Account Settings. You cannot cancel a subscription while If you buy a subscription, any unused, free trial time will be lost. apps.title: Aisle - Indian Dating App
apps.description: With more than 2.2M success stories, Aisle is the first date-to-marry app, imagined for Indians worldwide. It's for people who are done with endless swiping and are ready to find their life partner. If you're looking for a modern approach to matchmaking that perfectly blends modern outlooks with traditional sensibilities, then start your love story with Aisle. Over the years Aisle has become the largest community of vibrant Indians, South Asians, Desis, from around the world connecting online to go on meaningful offline dates. You can read beautiful stories of couples who met on Aisle at blog.aisle.co Why Aisle is the Top Choice for Meaningful Dating: Date-to-Marry Mindset: We’re built for people seeking serious relationships. Our users are high-intent singles who are genuinely ready for commitment and want to find their life partner. Verified Profiles, Real Connections: Every profile goes through a 2-step verification process to ensure authenticity and a safe dating experience. We check every profile so you can relax, knowing that Arjun from Bangalore is actually Arjun from Bangalore. Intent-Based Matching: Your mother tongue matters. Your Sunday routines matter. We match on the stuff that still matters 20 years from now. Our advanced algorithm considers your core values, life goals, mother tongue, faith and lifestyle - the essential elements that truly matter when building a future together. Features which helps us standout: Comments - Start a thoughtful conversation by responding to what caught your eye on someone's profile. Aisle Concierge - For those who mean business. Handpicked profiles, global reach, and advanced filters to find your match 2X faster. Private Browsing - Browse with complete control. Especially for women to date safely and confidently. Advanced Filters - Search for people based on lifestyle preferences and recent activity. Made for Indians, by Indians: Whether you're in Chennai or Chicago, we get why you need someone who understands both your Netflix queue and your family WhatsApp group. Join Millions of Success Stories: It's not about finding someone perfect - it's about finding someone perfect for you. What started as a dating app has grown into a community that proves commitment is what makes love last. In-App Purchases: Upgrade your experience with premium features. Aisle Plus: Unlimited likes to connect faster. Aisle Premium: Everything in Plus, with more tools to deepen your search. Aisle Concierge: The ultimate experience for high-intent marriage seekers. Subscriptions renew automatically. Cancel anytime via app settings, 24hrs before renewal. In the Press: “The Info Edge Effect: How Dating App Aisle’s Revenue Soared 146% After Acquisition” - Inc42 “Young Indians are moving away from casual dating and seeking more substantial relationships. Our platform has always catered to those looking for long-term connections, and we are seeing a notable uptick in interest” says Chandni Gaglani Head of Aisle to Deccanchronicle “InfoEdge backed dating app Aisle appoints Chandni Gaglani as Head of Aisle Network” - Your Story How Aisle used meme marketing to reinvent old-school romance - socialsamosa About Us: Aisle is a premium Indian dating app built for those looking for meaningful relationships. Founded in 2014, Aisle is operated by Aisle Network Pvt. Ltd., majority-owned by Info Edge (India) Ltd., the company behind Naukri, Jeevansathi, and 99acres - ensuring trust and reliability. Your personal data is processed securely, in line with our Privacy Policy and Terms & Conditions. Support: team@aisle.co Terms of Service: https://www.aisle.co/termsofuse.html Privacy Policy: https://www.aisle.co/privacypolicy.html

apps.title: Cuffed: Dating & Relationships
apps.description: CUFFED: EXCLUSIVE DATING, EXCLUSIVE MATCHES Welcome to Cuffed, a members-only dating app where you match with one match at a time. Our acceptance rate is low, but our match-to-meetup rate is high. We vet every member of our community to make sure you’re only swiping on people you’d actually be excited to go on a date with. When you match with someone on Cuffed, you’re only talking to each other—helping you date intentionally by letting you focus exclusively on the other person. No distractions, no endless small talk, no more treating dating like an email job. A dating app for authentic people with busy lives who don’t have time for endless swiping. Match and meet up, and if the vibes aren’t right, you can end the conversation or wait for the match timer to run out. Membership to Cuffed includes access to our singles events at our favorite bars & lounges. apps.description: Inner Circle is a curated members community for people who live ambitious, interesting lifestyles – and want to date people who move in the same circles. Built on the belief that opposites don’t attract, everything starts with two important questions: What are you interested in? And where do you spend your time? Our community is niche by design, and not everyone will be accepted. Each application is reviewed by our membership team to curate a community of people with shared lifestyles and who move in the same circles. Once approved, you'll be a guest in the community and can earn access to features like messaging by inviting friends. raw_data.description: The Best Sober Dating. Bar. None™ Overcome sobriety’s toughest challenges for singles – dating. Conquer sobriety with that special someone on Loosid’s Sober Dating. Since 2018, Loosid has initiated over 9.14M sessions and fostered more than 155,000 relationships. WHAT THEY’RE SAYING “If you want to take the pressure off a first date and meet someone interested in a hike, coffee - vs meeting for drinks - this is a great app.” “It's so hard to date when you’re sober and this app made me feel like I finally can try dating for real again.” “I’m a member on Loosid Community and saw they opened now for dating which is awesome. Great way to connect with like minded others.” HIGHLIGHTS Match with local sober singles near you Chat with your matches Stand out with Flirt and SuperLike Spot secret admirers Bookmark profiles that catch your eye SOBER QUESTIONS Navigating sobriety as a single person is tough – we know. Which is why we created Sober Questions to help you find what you’re looking for!: - “My idea of a perfect Sober Saturday…” - “The biggest gift sobriety has given to me is…” - “My favorite mocktail is…” Need help? Use our crisis hotline for immediate help and support. Loosid is the perfect dating app to help you stay on track and find the love of your life. Join for free today! Contact us: https://loosidapp.com/contact-us/ Privacy Policy: https://loosidapp.com/privacypolicy/ Terms of Use: https://loosidapp.com/terms-and-conditions/
